Game Notes:

Inspired by the adventure and imagination that 
we love from classic science-fiction, No Man's 
Sky presents you with a galaxy to explore, 
filled with unique planets and lifeforms, 
and constant danger and action. 

System Requirements:

Windows: 7 / 8 / 10 (64-bit only)
Processor: Core i3
Memory: 8GB RAM
Graphics: NVidia GTX 480, AMD Radeon 7870
Hard Drive: 10 GB
Mouse, Keyboard

For more info go to :    
https://www.gog.com/game/no_mans_sky

Update Info:

Patch 1287169 (19 August 2016) 

- An issue causing the game not to save after dying is fixed 
- A crash which occurred during warp is fixed 
- A crash in the scanning system is fixed 
- Phenom II processors crash fixed

Install Notes:

1. Download
2. Install the game
3. Run the game as administrator
4. Have fun
